des: This skill shows you how dolphins sound. Lean back and listen to the magnificent tones of any kind of dolphin. Wether it's a bottlenose dolphin, Amazon river dolphin, Risso’s dolphin or just a common dolphin. Learn the speech of cetaceans.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
